textBeforeTable: Playlist Tracks:  Our guests this morning were Jenny and Bethany of The Ericksons, joining us in studio the week of their release party for "The Wild" at the Cedar Cultural Center. We had a great conversation about songwriting, great women who have lit up the stage before them, and taking the next step in their music craft. We also heard new music from Joshua James and Vicky Emerson.   January 14, 2013   1/14/2013 Pam Without Boundaries Schedule About Events News Personalities Programs Support Us On Demand Listen Now
